    <hr style="border: 2px solid black">
    <p>Leif Erikson once served Lord Olaf Haraldsson, but after being persuaded by Ragnar Lothbrok, he joined his friends against Olaf Haraldsson. With a personality who likes to explore new places, after Ragnar Lothbrok became the patriarch Leif Erikson and 15 others set out to search for new lands. Leif Erikson became the first European to set foot in North America.</p>
